name: User clicks on station widget on home screen to redirect to station details screen
description: User Clicks on Station Widget on Home and redirects to station detail page
descriptionHtml: User Clicks on Station Widget on Home and redirects to station detail page

testStage.description: User Clicks on Station Widget on Home and redirects to station detail page

steps.name: I set the location of the device to "DENMARK_10150"
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I close and open application
I click on "STORES" button
I check that the "Stores Screen" is displayed
I click on "USER LOCATION" button
I click on "HOME" button
I close and open application
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I close and open application
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I accept Updated Terms and Conditions
I swipe on the device screen to the to refresh Home Page
I check that the "Station Widget" is displayed
I get the text from the "STATION WIDGET ADDRESS"
I click on "STATION WIDGET"
I check that the "Stores Details Back Button" is displayed
I check that the "Header Text" is displayed
I check that the "Google Map" is displayed
I get the text from the "STORE NAME"
I check that the application text: "Vallensbækvej 13" isn't empty
I get the text from the "STORE ADDRESS"
I check that the application text: "2605 Brøndby" isn't empty
I get the text from the "STORE DISTANCE"
I check that the application text: "1.3 km" isn't empty
I get the text from the "STORE OPEN STATUS"
I check that the application text: "Open" isn't empty
I get the text from the "STORE ADDRESS"
I check that the application text: "2605 Brøndby" is equals to expected value: "2605 Brøndby"
I get the text from the "STORE OPEN STATUS"
I check that the application text: "Open" isn't empty
I get the text from the "STORE ADDRESS"
I check that the application text: "2605 Brøndby" is equals to expected value: "2605 Brøndby"
I click on "Back button" CTA Store Details Page
I check that the "Station Widget" is displayed
I click on "STATION WIDGET DIRECTIONS CTA"
